<figcaption>Choose upgrades wisely — your build determines how you dominate the arena.</figcaption>
</figure>

<h2 id="faq">FAQ</h2>

<div class="tip-title">❓ Is Arrow Arena free to play?</div>
<p>Yes, Arrow Arena is completely free. It runs in your browser with no downloads required. Just open the game link and start playing.</p>

<div class="tip-title">❓ What devices can I play Arrow Arena on?</div>
<p>Arrow Arena works on desktop, mobile, and tablet browsers. It's built with HTML5 and Unity WebGL, so any modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge) should run it smoothly.</p>

<div class="tip-title">❓ How do charged shots work?</div>
<p>Hold the left mouse button to charge your arrow. The longer you hold, the more damage it deals. Release to fire. Fully charged shots can one-shot low-health opponents but leave you vulnerable while charging.</p>

<div class="tip-title">❓ What happens when I level up?</div>
<p>You get to choose from random skill upgrades. These change your archer's abilities — from bouncing arrows to multi-shot to explosive rounds. Different upgrades create different playstyles each match.</p>

<div class="tip-title">❓ Can I play with friends?</div>
<p>Arrow Arena is a multiplayer game where you join public matches. You can't create private lobbies currently, but you can team up informally with friends in the same public server.</p>

<div class="tip-title">❓ What's the best strategy for beginners?</div>
<p>Focus on survival first. Keep moving, farm crystals early to level up, and avoid aggressive players until you have good upgrades. Once you're higher level, you can hunt opponents more confidently.</p>

